<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-10606] PartitionUpdate.operationCount() return the wrong number of operation for compact tables</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10606</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For compact tables &lt;tt&gt;PartitionUpdate.operationCount()&lt;/tt&gt; return the wrong number of operation as it does not take into operation on static rows.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12908378">CASSANDRA-10606</key>
            <summary>PartitionUpdate.operationCount() return the wrong number of operation for compact tables</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
